    Launch wrappers for the desktop menu and command line have been
    provided to conveniently switch to Filmic Blender.

    Adjustments can be found under the "Color Management" section.

    For 2.79 see:
      https://docs.blender.org/manual/en/2.79/render/post_process/color_management.html?highlight=color%20management#settings

    For 3.x see:
      https://docs.blender.org/manual/en/2.83/render/color_management.html?highlight=color%20management#settings
  -->
  <upstream>
    <bugs-to>https://github.com/sobotka/filmic-blender/issues</bugs-to>
